<br>
My play time is kinda screwy. Most often I can get on a couple times a week for 2 hours or so. Once or twice a week I can get on longer for guild events or raids, but primarily I guess you'd say I solo.  I know this is changined recently but in the past I got really crappy experience when grouped so I soloed to &quot;keep up&quot;.<br>
<br>
I'm 60 now with no epic and my gear is kinda ok but not great.  My bank account is under 1k.  I have 2 (yes only 2) AA points. My plan is to sit in FG when soloing, pad 60 a bit (just in case) and once I'm comfortable that I have enough padding just push AA till I feel like my brain is going to explode. Naturally I'll still group whenever a group situation is available and I really do prefer the planes lately. <br>
<br>
So here's the point of all this explanation. Does it sound like a good plan?  AA till brain meltdown in FG?  Don't push to 61 till I'm pretty happy with AA progress?  <br>
<br>
 <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica" size="+1">Perilbane Mooncaster</font><br>
<font face="Arial, Helvetica" size="-1">Arch Mage of the 60th Circle<br>
Master Summoner of Essentially useless junk.</font></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=perilbane>Perilbane</A> at: 12/13/02 1:47:13 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xalmat@themagicianstower>Xalmat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 464<br> <font color=#333333>(12/13/02 3:21:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=326.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Seeking magely advice and opinions...</span><hr size=1> At 60, you lose a full yellow per death. But a 96% rez fixes that up nicely.<br>
<br>
I saw no reason to ding 61 until i got Ward of Xegony. And at 61, 33% of the shrooms are light blue.<br>
<br>
If you plan on hunting (grouping) in tier 2 planes (Storms, Valor), 65 all the way. But if you wanna solo, i'd stay 60 or 61 for now.<br>
<br>
AA moves so incredibly fast at 60+ its rediculous.<br>
<br>
